Cell["\<\
One should be careful about the ranges of the Euler angles. The returned \
Euler angles {\[Alpha],\[Beta],\[Gamma]} are limited to: -\[Pi]<\[Alpha],\
\[Gamma]<\[Pi], 0<\[Beta]<\[Pi].\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1349924290,ExpressionUUID->"ba4d6e1a-d9fc-4be1-bda1-6ec68e3f78e5"],

